# Markdown
- Do not add a blank line after headings — put the next paragraph, list, or code block directly under the heading
- No need for periods at the end of bullet points
- Prettify tables: pad cells so the `|` pipes align vertically across all rows
- Prefer short fenced-code language tags (e.g. `ts` not `typescript`)
